152
00:14:40,654 --> 00:14:42,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you're the best,</b></font>

153
00:14:42,494 --> 00:14:46,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>defeating him with that FR-killer rule!</b></font>

154
00:14:46,124 --> 00:14:48,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're nothing short of a genius!</b></font>

155
00:14:48,134 --> 00:14:49,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki...</b></font>

156
00:14:49,734 --> 00:14:53,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I really wanted to win
that race, no matter what.</b></font>

157
00:14:53,934 --> 00:14:58,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He pissed me off, but that's not why.</b></font>

158
00:14:58,404 --> 00:15:00,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just didn't want to lose the race.</b></font>

159
00:15:00,804 --> 00:15:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had never felt that way before during a race.</b></font>

160
00:15:04,014 --> 00:15:07,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're becoming more like a real street racer.</b></font>

161
00:15:07,484 --> 00:15:10,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A street racer? No, it's not like that.</b></font>

162
00:15:10,654 --> 00:15:13,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll refine my skills when I get out of here</b></font>

163
00:15:13,954 --> 00:15:18,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so that I won't embarrass you
and our Akina "Levin Trueno" team.</b></font>

164
00:15:19,624 --> 00:15:21,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What were you talking about?</b></font>

165
00:15:21,594 --> 00:15:23,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, nothing...</b></font>

166
00:15:23,164 --> 00:15:26,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, how is Saori?</b></font>

167
00:15:26,134 --> 00:15:28,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm worried about her.</b></font>

168
00:15:28,034 --> 00:15:30,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's fine. She says hi.</b></font>

169
00:15:30,834 --> 00:15:32,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cool!</b></font>

170
00:15:32,674 --> 00:15:36,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I get out of here, all four
of us can go for a drive again!</b></font>

171
00:15:36,974 --> 00:15:39,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--Yeah.</b></font>

172
00:15:41,784 --> 00:15:44,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm glad that Itsuki is okay.</b></font>

173
00:15:44,454 --> 00:15:48,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. His Eight-Five should be back soon, too.</b></font>

174
00:15:48,794 --> 00:15:52,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lied about something.</b></font>

175
00:15:52,494 --> 00:15:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Saori was shaken up so
badly after the accident</b></font>

176
00:15:57,294 --> 00:16:01,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that she doesn't want to
think about it ever again.</b></font>

177
00:16:02,674 --> 00:16:04,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hmm...</b></font>

178
00:16:04,574 --> 00:16:08,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So she knows that he's a nice person,</b></font>

179
00:16:08,914 --> 00:16:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it wouldn't work out between them.</b></font>

180
00:16:14,184 --> 00:16:15,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Practice Guide"</b></font>

181
00:16:14,354 --> 00:16:18,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Saori isn't coming to see me...</b></font>

182
00:16:21,824 --> 00:16:23,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Darn it!</b></font>

183
00:16:23,724 --> 00:16:26,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A street racer doesn't need a girlfriend!</b></font>

184
00:16:39,174 --> 00:16:42,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What brought you here tonight?</b></font>

185
00:16:42,244 --> 00:16:44,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was on my way to an ATM</b></font>

186
00:16:44,014 --> 00:16:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and thought I would stop
by to see your ugly face.</b></font>

187
00:16:48,514 --> 00:16:52,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi banged it up pretty good, didn't he?</b></font>

188
00:16:52,224 --> 00:16:55,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course, with that race, he couldn't help it.</b></font>

189
00:16:55,454 --> 00:17:00,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That idiot... but he's heading
in the right direction.</b></font>

190
00:17:00,064 --> 00:17:04,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have a smile on your face
after he messed up your fender?</b></font>

191
00:17:04,294 --> 00:17:07,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His style is changing.</b></font>

192
00:17:07,134 --> 00:17:11,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was good before, but there
was something missing.</b></font>

193
00:17:11,604 --> 00:17:14,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lately, he's going faster.</b></font>

194
00:17:14,974 --> 00:17:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He stepped it up a notch.</b></font>

195
00:17:16,974 --> 00:17:18,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can you tell, Bunta?</b></font>

196
00:17:18,984 --> 00:17:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you see this Eight-Six
day in and day out,</b></font>

197
00:17:23,554 --> 00:17:25,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can tell how he's driving.</b></font>

198
00:17:25,654 --> 00:17:28,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess that makes sense.</b></font>

199
00:17:33,264 --> 00:17:37,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll stop by on my way back.
Let's have a drink tonight.</b></font>

200
00:17:37,094 --> 00:17:38,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

201
00:17:46,244 --> 00:17:48,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi is crazy...</b></font>

202
00:17:48,344 --> 00:17:50,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but his dad's just as crazy.</b></font>

203
00:17:50,614 --> 00:17:52,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hasn't changed a bit.</b></font>

204
00:18:15,604 --> 00:18:22,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Mountain Kamameshi Bowl"</b></font>

205
00:18:26,184 --> 00:18:29,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just can't help it...</i></b></font>

206
00:18:31,984 --> 00:18:36,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Not that I expect anything,</i>
<i>but I can't just pass by...</i></b></font>

207
00:18:58,684 --> 00:19:02,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, I'm not a crazy person or anything...</b></font>

208
00:19:02,714 --> 00:19:05,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was just wondering
what's wrong with your car.</b></font>

209
00:19:05,754 --> 00:19:09,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no idea what's going on in there.</b></font>

210
00:19:09,524 --> 00:19:13,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how much I turn the
ignition, the engine won't start.</b></font>

211
00:19:13,194 --> 00:19:16,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can take a look at it, if you don't mind.</b></font>

212
00:19:16,494 --> 00:19:18,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd appreciate it.</b></font>

213
00:19:18,504 --> 00:19:22,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like something electrical...</b></font>

214
00:19:22,334 --> 00:19:24,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's see...</b></font>

215
00:19:29,544 --> 00:19:31,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>S13...</i></b></font>

216
00:19:33,214 --> 00:19:35,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Speed Stars.</i></b></font>

217
00:19:35,884 --> 00:19:38,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch.</b></font>

218
00:19:38,224 --> 00:19:40,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What do you think?
--Well...</b></font>

219
00:19:50,134 --> 00:19:52,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My face has never been this close</i></b></font>

220
00:19:52,634 --> 00:19:54,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>to a woman other than my mother.</i></b></font>

221
00:19:54,734 --> 00:19:57,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My heart can't take this...</i></b></font>

222
00:19:57,734 --> 00:20:00,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She is so cute!</i></b></font>

223
00:20:07,414 --> 00:20:09,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What a nice smell!</i></b></font>

224
00:20:09,414 --> 00:20:14,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm smelling a cute girl</i>
<i>for the first time in my life.</i></b></font>

225
00:20:14,594 --> 00:20:19,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no! I hope I don't smell like sweat!</i></b></font>

226
00:20:31,174 --> 00:20:33,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, it should start now.</b></font>

227
00:20:33,674 --> 00:20:35,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go ahead and try the ignition.</b></font>

228
00:20:40,814 --> 00:20:42,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good!</b></font>

229
00:20:42,114 --> 00:20:45,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, it started! Amazing!</b></font>

230
00:20:45,284 --> 00:20:47,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much for your help.</b></font>

231
00:20:47,284 --> 00:20:49,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You saved me.</b></font>

232
00:20:50,354 --> 00:20:53,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it was nothing.</b></font>

233
00:20:53,164 --> 00:20:54,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true.</b></font>

234
00:20:54,794 --> 00:20:59,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I respect guys who are good
with mechanical stuff.</b></font>

235
00:20:59,034 --> 00:21:01,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to thank you later, so...</b></font>

236
00:21:01,634 --> 00:21:04,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...can I have your number?</b></font>

237
00:21:04,704 --> 00:21:08,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about it, really.</b></font>

238
00:21:08,274 --> 00:21:10,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay...</b></font>

239
00:21:10,114 --> 00:21:13,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no!</i></b></font>

240
00:21:13,114 --> 00:21:17,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This could be the only chance I'll ever get!</i></b></font>

241
00:21:20,454 --> 00:21:24,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm such an idiot! An idiot! I'm an idiot!</i></b></font>

242
00:21:24,964 --> 00:21:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me?</b></font>

243
00:21:26,664 --> 00:21:28,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

244
00:21:29,394 --> 00:21:31,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here.</b></font>

245
00:21:32,864 --> 00:21:36,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My name is Mako Sato. Call me!</b></font>

246
00:22:05,534 --> 00:22:09,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I stood there for thirty minutes</i></b></font>

247
00:22:09,234 --> 00:22:12,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>wondering what had just happened.</i></b></font>

248
00:22:12,074 --> 00:22:14,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't a dream!</b></font>

249
00:22:15,074 --> 00:22:19,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I happened to run into an angel</i></b></font>

250
00:22:19,114 --> 00:22:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>under the Kamameshi billboard.</i></b></font>

251
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was a time when I</i>
<i>wandered aimlessly, tired of love</i></b></font>

252
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost sight of myself and gave in to desire</i></b></font>

253
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But destiny is ever-changing</i></b></font>

254
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And charmed by innocent eyes</i></b></font>

255
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I hold you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

256
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All I can say is that I believe</i>
<i>my feelings are true</i></b></font>

257
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's enjoy our happiness...</i></b></font>

258
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Into our shining future</i></b></font>

259
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We'll prove countless times...</i></b></font>

260
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Our passion will last for eternity!</i></b></font>

261
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom like a red rose,</i>
<i>I embrace you ever so tightly</i></b></font>

262
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I lose everything that I have,</i>
<i>I will never let you go</i></b></font>

263
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bloom, my beautiful...</i></b></font>

264
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...and miraculous flower</i></b></font>

265
00:24:26,504 --> 00:24:30,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You appeared before me</i>
<i>suddenly in the bright light.</i></b></font>

266
00:24:30,514 --> 00:24:35,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And I instantly became a puppet</i>
<i>by your blinding beauty!</i></b></font>

267
00:24:35,014 --> 00:24:36,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's wrong, Iketani?</i></b></font>

268
00:24:36,584 --> 00:24:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can no longer live without you!</i></b></font>

269
00:24:39,024 --> 00:24:42,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You have become my queen,</i>
<i>my angel, who controls my mind!</i></b></font>

270
00:24:42,824 --> 00:24:46,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's deep in his own world...</i></b></font>

271
00:24:46,594 --> 00:24:49,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: "The Angel of Usui."</i></b></font>

272
00:24:49,334 --> 00:24:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The angel?! Oh, my Mako!</i></b></font>

273
00:24:52,864 --> 00:24:54,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

